node.text: After my session with @doc.chandon yesterday I’ve had lots of time to think. Today during my workout I felt a rush of excitement and jolt of focus take over my body. I’m responsible for my life! I’m not saying that you have to go through this journey alone, but I am saying that you have to take responsibility for your choices. Sometimes we can doubt ourselves and look to others for help when all we really need is to look deep within ourselves for the answers. Sometimes we can’t find the answers because we surround ourselves with so many distractions that it becomes too noisy in our minds. Give yourself time and quiet your mind enough to listen to what you really need to hear!! Sending my love 😍
